<td>Quick announcement: the 8 year veteran reward has been decided!  It's called Throne of Heroes and will port 8 year vets directly to the throne room in the guild lobby.  ToH will be similar to Origin in regards to its casting and reuse timers.  To accommodate this new ability, the guild lobby and its amenities will be made available to everyone, even those who are not yet flagged for Dragons of Norrath.  <br />
 <br />
Looking forward to 8 more,<br />
Oshran <br />
<br />
